data.description: Experience unparalleled luxury in this Silvestri built 5-level split home. Boasting 3,752 sq ft above grade and 1,177 sq ft below grade, this masterpiece offers 4 bedrooms, 4 full and 2 half baths. New Roof, 2023. Quality craftsmanship is evident throughout the open floor plan, highlighted by a spacious kitchen connected to a formal dinning room with wainscoting walls and tray ceiling and a soaring two-story great room. The master en suite is a private retreat with an oversized closet and a lavish bathroom adorned with granite, tile, and a spacious shower. The two lower levels offer additional living space that could be additional bedrooms, media, play or recreation rooms.Step outside to an exquisite covered outdoor living space w/ gas fireplace. New carpet throughout.
